SBTProjectSourceLayout
Same as Maven defaults
    src/
        main/
            resources/
                <files to include in main jar here>
            scala/
                <main Scala sources>
            java/
                <main Java sources>
        test/
            resources
                <files to include in test jar here>
            scala/
                <test Scala sources>
            java/
                <test Java sources>

Play projects do things a little differently
